Its promise is that dev teams will be able to adapt / deploy applications quickly and flexibly. But what is often lost in considering this architectural path is the increased complexity that comes as a result of the explosion in the number of APIs and the number of potential connections/dependencies along with it.
Given the increased complexity and the inherent difficulties in ensuring API quality, what steps can Accenture teams take to ensure rock-solid quality in microservices applications?
